%91n/author-sJH7A_ZQdhEDn2fVhapctw">Hà Tốn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/Ngh%C4%A9-c%E1%BB%95-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-uKgIyVSc39mzt7MwKXJJJg">Nghĩ cổ kỳ 4 - 拟古其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%ADch/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%C3%ACnh-x%E1%BB%AD-s%C4%A9/poem-8F8m2hsTSbF5cbiFl1EFsA">Tặng Trình xử sĩ - 贈程處士</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%ADch/author-0g7JqAcYihMIfY-BKbTDYA">Vương Tích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-U%E1%BA%A9n/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%AF-qu%C3%A1n/poem-_ViUz2Bfh7uhO0UxGCmmdg">Thu dạ lữ quán - 秋夜旅館</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-U%E1%BA%A9n/author-FEMBL5dfX_ll7x4mFJ88jA">Doãn Uẩn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
